="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fifty-fiftys-keena-drops-lawsuit-against-attrakt-returns-to-label-3516206">《五十五十》之后的 Keena 撤销了对 Attrakt 的诉讼，回归厂牌，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
